data.description: HUGE PRICE IMPROVEMENT! Family home nestled in the heart of Normandy! Boasting around 2000 SF with 3 bedrooms, and 2 full baths & mostly finished LL. With incredible potential, and gain of equity to be had, you will DEFinitely want to see this house! A FANTASTIC opportunity to own a place where life is a little sweeter & quieter. Under NEW plush carpeting, you’ll discover original wood in two bedrooms & the Living Room ready for you to refinish if you desire. Home freshly painted throughout. Home is light and bright, perfect for any gathering or simply relaxing. Your eat-in kitchen offers ample quartz counters, custom cabinetry, PANTRY & appliances! Breezeway is perfect for Office, Dining, & Add'l living space. Step outside to be wowed by your generous yard, extending over 1/3 ACRE, featuring front AND back patios. LL hosts HUGE Family Room, full bath, Laundry & much Storage. Walking distance to Library, UMSL, & Greenway/Parks! W/D, dishwasher & Fridge included and NEW Garage door too.
